Furthermore, while both ideas use human validation and aim for ecological validity, Idea 0's construction of challenge probes based on a taxonomy derived from retracted papers and meta-research on scientific flaws represents a unique grounding in real-world scientific error types—an angle not addressed in Papers 1–5.

